    {"id":"t-D-body","type":"text","x":1175,"y":135,"width":310,"height":300,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"seed":16,"version":1,"versionNonce":16,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1747200000000,"link":null,"locked":false,"text":"ai-wiki wordt één tenant in\nde ai-consultant-stack.\n\nFirestore vervangt git als\nSoT. GCS voor attachments.\nVertex RAG over de hele\ncorpus. zotero-mcp + nieuwe\nwiki-mcp delen schema.\n\nGit/Quartz blijft als\nexport-laag voor publicatie.\n\nDelta tov vandaag:\n• GCP-project + IAM\n• Schema-migratie\n• 2-way sync git ↔ Firestore\n• Verlies van \"markdown-\n  in-git is alles\"-discipline","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"ai-wiki wordt één tenant in\nde ai-consultant-stack.\n\nFirestore vervangt git als\nSoT. GCS voor attachments.\nVertex RAG over de hele\ncorpus. zotero-mcp + nieuwe\nwiki-mcp delen schema.\n\nGit/Quartz blijft als\nexport-laag voor publicatie.\n\nDelta tov vandaag:\n• GCP-project + IAM\n• Schema-migratie\n• 2-way sync git ↔ Firestore\n• Verlies van \"markdown-\n  in-git is alles\"-discipline","lineHeight":1.4},
    {"id":"t-D-score","type":"text","x":1175,"y":445,"width":310,"height":60,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#c92a2a","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"seed":17,"version":1,"versionNonce":17,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1747200000000,"link":null,"locked":false,"text":"Feas: LAAG    Maint: HOOG\nValue: LAAG (overkill voor 1 user)\nScore: 3 + 2 + 3 = 8","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Feas: LAAG    Maint: HOOG\nValue: LAAG (overkill voor 1 user)\nScore: 3 + 2 + 3 = 8","lineHeight":1.4},

    {"id":"t-reco","type":"text","x":80,"y":540,"width":1420,"height":120,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"#fff9db","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"seed":18,"version":1,"versionNonce":18,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1747200000000,"link":null,"locked":false,"text":"Aanbeveling — A + C in fasering. A is laagste-hangende-fruit (saved manual werk per ingest). C voegt machine-leesbaarheid toe zonder schema-verschuiving. Beide composeerbaar; \nelk is ~1 week werk geïsoleerd. B alleen verdedigbaar als Zotero-gebruik echt aktief wordt (>5 nieuwe bronnen/week). D pas overwegen als ai-wiki multi-user wordt — vandaag niet.","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Aanbeveling — A + C in fasering. A is laagste-hangende-fruit (saved manual werk per ingest). C voegt machine-leesbaarheid toe zonder schema-verschuiving. Beide composeerbaar; \nelk is ~1 week werk geïsoleerd. B alleen verdedigbaar als Zotero-gebruik echt aktief wordt (>5 nieuwe bronnen/week). D pas overwegen als ai-wiki multi-user wordt — vandaag niet.","lineHeight":1.4}
